                    <span>I had to read this book as a requirement for my AP English IV course. I must say that Vonnegut does an extremely good job of explaining the meaning of life using the most finite, human terms possible. A great read for anybody.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">One of Vonnegut's Best.</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
